OL,4,CUAE could be torturing detained
OL,5,Cactivists, UN says
OL,6, A group of activists detained in the
OL,7, United Arab Emirates (UAE) are enduring
OL,8, conditions that may amount to torture,
OL,9, a UN expert says.
OL,11,FUN Special Rapporteur Mary Lawlor says
OL,12,Fthe five detainees are being held in
OL,13,Fsolitary confinement for long periods
OL,14,Fand had their air conditioning switched
OL,15,Foff in temperatures above 40C.
OL,17,FShe called for them to be immediately
OL,18,Freleased after eight years in jail.
OL,20,FThe Emirati authorities have not
OL,21,Fresponded to the allegations.
